{"tid":276224,"cid":27,"subCid":0,"title":"召集所有想一齊玩board game嘅朋友","createTime":"2017-06-08T15:54:43.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-07T05:45:58.000Z","uid":77470,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"a2cd45f74c7b1aa54ac40edfe29f354d5f2d0a84","tid":276224,"uid":77470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T15:54:43.000Z","msg":"歡迎各位有興趣玩唔同種類board game嘅朋友仔加入<br />\n無論你係想玩網上版嘅board game<br />\n例如board game arena 或者 tabletop simulator<br />\n抑或係想出黎玩實體版board game我地都無任歡迎架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔識玩都唔緊要，大家可以一齊學<br />\n我都係學習階段<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有興趣嘅請留下你嘅嘅telegram id<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSeGK9EDh1X9Jtc4Js_iAoQOTCapSd4-GLjTkzJlvzRlybtMLA/viewform\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fforms%2Fd%2Fe%2F1FAIpQLSeGK9EDh1X9Jtc4Js_iAoQOTCapSd4-GLjTkzJlvzRlybtMLA%2Fviewform&d=uOAYi3c9FJurCftt%2FpsdAZZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=24900f29\" target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSeGK9EDh1X9Jtc4Js_iAoQOTCapSd4-GLjTkzJlvzRlybtMLA/viewform</a>"},{"pid":"fdfa56154333e5dbccb5065fcdab66e01d76cefb","tid":276224,"uid":77470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T16:24:19.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"95284a47149bccb490de14e7b3780889d2b65f93","tid":276224,"uid":1720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T16:38:21.000Z","msg":"想問依加有幾多人一齊玩 ?同埋如果約出黎玩 會係邊同歡唔歡迎毒L<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d506dffe4200481e7cf495438ca340988cd4121c","tid":276224,"uid":1720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T16:39:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>想問依加有幾多人一齊玩 ?同埋如果約出黎玩 會係邊同歡唔歡迎毒L<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n利申:新手 淨係被fd水過玩過幾次"},{"pid":"ce8daea7ee50e90a62be67b197d90ad51866b388","tid":276224,"uid":77470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T16:50:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>想問依加有幾多人一齊玩 ?同埋如果約出黎玩 會係邊同歡唔歡迎毒L<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n乜人都歡迎<br />\n只要你真係為左玩board game<br />\n個群新開未有乜人住<br />\n至於係邊到玩，我諗主要都集中係旺角或者觀塘果頭掛<br />\n但如果群內有人住得近想自組團幾個落樓下玩亦無任歡迎"},{"pid":"227848a48dd5d1fe253b5b3c998a00c28f84c113","tid":276224,"uid":77470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T17:37:58.000Z","msg":"推，等多少少人先一次過加"},{"pid":"d04453bf021fd304b9e1440807af259031420fc2","tid":276224,"uid":77470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T23:23:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"de90a06543145d2321582daaca029b86c5fba80e","tid":276224,"uid":89023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T23:58:05.000Z","msg":"其實 連登已經有幾個board game gp on telegram<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1bd543d44e3ac4366f8c116bb1d351bb89fb113","tid":276224,"uid":77470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T00:41:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實 連登已經有幾個board game gp on telegram<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都有見過，但好似都好耐之前，部份已經冇晒人出聲<br />\n同埋好似冇乜見過有人提會用bga 或者 tabletop黎玩"},{"pid":"04b48cc5706cde566e1f9261de866e8dedbb4d49","tid":276224,"uid":77470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T01:32:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6bd7e2a0ff94bb9fd8e5baaad2bfa36b46910b66","tid":276224,"uid":77470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T02:27:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ccaef2591070d2f6bfd0186770f7fa1b6d232320","tid":276224,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T02:28:22.000Z","msg":"純文字討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e1ce1c6639ea3636727a6fdcaea8fc395df33ce","tid":276224,"uid":77470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"